)\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 16}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?\u8220?\u8216?Maldito aquele que tratar seu pai ou sua m\u227?e com desprezo.\u8217? (E todo o povo dir\u225?: \u8216?Am\u233?m!\u8217?)\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 17}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?\u8220?\u8216?Maldito aquele que mudar de lugar os marcos divis\u243?rios do terreno do seu vizinho.\u8217? (E todo o povo dir\u225?: \u8216?Am\u233?m!\u8217?)\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 18}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?\u8220?\u8216?Maldito aquele que fizer um cego se perder no caminho.\u8217? (E todo o povo dir\u225?: \u8216?Am\u233?m!\u8217?)\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 19}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?\u8220?\u8216?Maldito aquele que perverter o julgamento de um residente estrangeiro, de um \u243?rf\u227?o}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11  ou de uma vi\u250?va.\u8217? (E todo o povo dir\u225?: \u8216?Am\u233?m!\u8217?)\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 20}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?\u8220?\u8216?Maldito aquele que se deitar com a esposa do seu pai, pois ele desonra seu pai.\u8217?}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11  (E todo o povo dir\u225?: \u8216?Am\u233?m!\u8217?)\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033