\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Segundo o n\u250?mero dos filhos de Israel.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 9}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?Pois o povo de Jeov\u225? \u233? sua por\u231?\u227?o,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Jac\u243? \u233? sua heran\u231?a.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 10}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?Ele o achou numa terra deserta,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Num deserto vazio, cheio de\u160?uivos.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Cercou-o para resguard\u225?-lo, cuidou dele,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 E o protegeu como a menina do seu olho.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 11}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?Assim como a \u225?guia ati\u231?a a\u160?ninhada,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Paira sobre os seus filhotes\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 E estende as asas para apanh\u225?-los,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Carregando-os nas suas penas,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 12}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?Somente Jeov\u225? o}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af